title: Slendytubbies V2 Beta [16+]
description: Slendytubbies is a Slender remake involving Teletubbies, instead of Slender man, and the nameless hero being chased. The game has many features that make it stand out from the rest such as multiplayer either where you play against other people to see who can get 10 custards first without being caught or where one player is the Slendytubby, and he or she must hunt down and capture all the other players before they can get 10 Teletubby Custards. Another great feature of the game is customizable skins to add that special Flair to your Teletubby. Featuring 3 Difficulties Morning, Dusk, and Night depends on how scary your game is.
